<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM10.3">
<l>kōvai maṇāṭṭi nīyuṉ koḻuṅkaṉi koṇṭemmai</l>
<l>āvi tolaiviyēl vāyaḻa kartammai yañcutum</l>
<l>pāviyēṉ ṟōṉṟip pāmpaṇai yārkkuntam pāmpupōl</l>
<l>nāvu miraṇṭuḷa vāyttu nāṇili yēṉukkē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O lady kōvai-creeper! Do not finish off my life with your plump fruit!</l>
<l>I am afraid of the beautiful-mouthed [Lord]!</l>
<l>Since [the day] I, a sinner, was born, He with the snake bed has had</l>
<l>two tongues, [just] like his snake, with regards to shameless me!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
